<p><em>Unless otherwise stated, any graphics or images in my articles are made and/or taken by me.</em></p>
<p><em><sub>This machine:</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>Listen to her heartbeat</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>She’ll sing eternally</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>This machine</sub></em><br />
<em><sub>Oh, titan can you hear me?</sub></em><br />
<em><sub><a href="https://youtu.be/T9cho6hluf0">Grant me eternal sleep.</a></sub></em></p>
<hr />
<p>Coldpost. Sequel to <a href="/the-fine-print">my D-class contest tale.</a></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show</a></div>
