<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>Why second-person?</strong></p>
<p>Because it's not about Teresa, it's about you. Teresa is a file of information, not a person; the person died years ago. Teresa is one of thousands of files. You could easily be one of them.</p>
</div>
