			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2726234">
									

<p>This is sooooo fucked up and I love it. Just the idea of someone's memory and identity being twisted like that is just&#8230; horrifying. I think the second-person perspective helped to reinforce a feeling of something being just off, something being wrong, which I think works extremely well here. Additionally, the writing, especially in the beginning gave me a Douglas Adams feeling, which I appreciated.</p>

