														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2727818">
									

<p>I wholeheartedly approve of this adaptation. I even recognized Gears just from his dispassionate professionalism. This is a brilliant realization of the human cost of SCP-2000, and I hope to see more tales that explore that cost in such a vivid way.</p>
