			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2727985">
									

<p>I, for one, enjoyed the second person perspective. It's a staple of CYOA novels and adventure games of all stripes, and though it can be hard to pull off in prose, I think it did wonders here for not only immersion, but in really selling the coldness of the Foundation.</p>
